{"tid":584731,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"涉電梯偷拍16歲少女裙底　休班警拒認罪","createTime":"2018-03-08T04:57:14.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-08T05:04:29.000Z","uid":20933,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"9876e6d44b8e54e3d9f24c7684c4dc492165ea2c","tid":584731,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-08T04:57:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/08/125703_431b7ea47ffac05c11896a7f833f91cc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F08%2F125703_431b7ea47ffac05c11896a7f833f91cc.jpg&h=fc9866f7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n男警去年1月休班時在港鐵旺角站的扶手電梯，涉嫌偷拍16歲少女裙底春光，警方事隔一年落案起訴他一項有違公德罪，案件今(8日)在西九龍法院答辯，被告否認控罪，裁判官將案排期於5月23日開審，預計審訊3天。<br />\n<br />\n報稱警員的34歲被告英裕泰，案發時駐守水警西分區巡邏小隊。控罪指他在2017年1月21日在港鐵旺角站的扶手電梯上，作出性質猥褻、淫褻及令人憎惡的有違公德行為，即重複地將其右腳踏前至女事主X的裙底範圍內，用以拍攝X的裙底影片。"},{"pid":"3343af735d6c72119fc96095df8683280bb953c9","tid":584731,"uid":36964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-08T05:00:02.000Z","msg":"休班警<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  休班警<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  休班警<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  休班警<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  休班警<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  休班警<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  休班警<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  休班警<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3bc40195397d60e006db5d72fac0bff2e6031b77","tid":584731,"uid":170711,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-08T05:01:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6c46c60518f8cdd3d40411d373027c8272758533","tid":584731,"uid":35014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-08T05:04:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}